  <p>
  The XML Contentbase Connector (XCC) is an interface to communicate with MarkLogic Server from a Java or .NET middleware application layer.
  It provides APIs for 
    <ul>
      <li>Evaluating stored XQuery programs</li>
      <li>Dynamic construction and evaluation of XQuery programs from Java (or .Net) code</li>
      <li>Type marshalling</li>
      <li>Document management and streaming inserts</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

